{"tid":961130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解班傻9 鍾意打邊爐同韓燒，出去畀錢但又要自己煮","createTime":"2018-12-29T21:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T08:16:04.000Z","uid":110375,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a50fa656995a09c0f2404837801769f7c21b2443","tid":961130,"uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T21:22:27.000Z","msg":"首先唔講好高級嗰啲<br />\n同普通水平嘅韓國燒烤銅打邊爐<br />\n畀二百幾三百蚊去食啲垃圾原材料仲要自己煮 又冇營養<br />\n<br />\n238蚊去食個西餐仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日講埋啲戇鳩藉口乜嘢打邊爐可以圍埋一齊傾下偈， 食西餐咁可以圍埋一齊傾計啦<br />\n<br />\n最戇鳩係畀人賺到笑， 廚師都唔使請 淨係買定啲原材料畀個煲就散你幾舊<br />\n<br />\n喺啲亞洲人先鍾意玩埋啲咁嘅嘢， 要燒烤鬼佬自己係屋企玩bbq就得啦"},{"pid":"014f9fa0e96e60e9e56dc77a1703e816a52bba6f","tid":961130,"uid":20066,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T21:41:31.000Z","msg":"樓主冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b517a202cd543c620b814c920e84b690823ae4","tid":961130,"uid":110375,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"014f9fa0e96e60e9e56dc77a1703e816a52bba6f","tid":961130,"uid":20066,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T21:41:31.000Z","msg":"樓主冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T22:15:16.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩嘅一大班朋友一定要打邊爐㗎咩"},{"pid":"800557ba3371f2625cd9fdd1d97adf96357ce4f8","tid":961130,"uid":129821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T22:17:20.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好咁傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad236c4de9f4373be7b02b8dd33d2749d911a8c8","tid":961130,"uid":151969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b2b517a202cd543c620b814c920e84b690823ae4","tid":961130,"uid":110375,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"014f9fa0e96e60e9e56dc77a1703e816a52bba6f","tid":961130,"uid":20066,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T21:41:31.000Z","msg":"樓主冇朋友<img src=\